name: MyTechHelp
overview:
myTechHelp offers specialized technical assistance online and by phone to consumers and small businesses across all computing and communication devices as well as software applications, hardware and other technology. Providing on-demand support to over 170,000 subscription-based customers and hundreds of instant fix services each day, myTechHelp services the United States and Canada. Support services were made available to the United Kingdom in December 2012.

myTechHelp redefines the way technical assistance is delivered, getting consumers up and running quickly without the inconvenience of having to leave their home. No longer do consumers have to deal with multiple support providers associated with each individual device or software application they own. Customers can depend on myTechHelp to resolve their technology concerns regardless of brand, make or model. Offering a comprehensive suite of services including support for virus detection and repair, data recovery, new device configuration, home networking, software and device installation, cloud services and more, myTechHelp has positioned itself as the leading provider of remote technical support.
